text: Iktisad () is a rural locality (a village) in Utyakovsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 7 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Krasnousolsky, 4 km from Utyakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Iktisad
